{
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s01",
      "text": "She teaches AI to think.",
      "rate": "-10%",
      "duration": 2.16,
      "video_start": 0.3
    },
    {
      "id": "s02",
      "text": "This is Yao Fu.",
      "rate": "-5%",
      "duration": 1.44,
      "video_start": 3.5
    },
    {
      "id": "s02b",
      "text": "Most engineers write answers. She writes the questions.",
      "rate": "-5%",
      "duration": 3.696,
      "video_start": 5.5
    },
    {
      "id": "s03",
      "text": "Every day, she tests where AI fails \u2014 on earnings, on risk, on reasoning.",
      "rate": "+0%",
      "duration": 5.856,
      "video_start": 9.2
    },
    {
      "id": "s04a",
      "text": "Faster than her.",
      "rate": "+0%",
      "duration": 1.224,
      "video_start": 15.2
    },
    {
      "id": "s04b",
      "text": "In some ways, smarter.",
      "rate": "+0%",
      "duration": 1.776,
      "video_start": 17.0
    },
    {
      "id": "s05",
      "text": "But one day, the AI asked her something she couldn't answer.",
      "rate": "-15%",
      "duration": 4.32,
      "video_start": 20.5
    },
    {
      "id": "s05b",
      "text": "It asked: Why does beauty matter to you?",
      "rate": "-15%",
      "duration": 3.024,
      "video_start": 25.4
    },
    {
      "id": "s06a",
      "text": "She showed it a sunset. It described the wavelengths perfectly.",
      "rate": "-10%",
      "duration": 4.104,
      "video_start": 29.0
    },
    {
      "id": "s06b",
      "text": "But it couldn't tell her why it was beautiful.",
      "rate": "-10%",
      "duration": 2.64,
      "video_start": 34.0
    },
    {
      "id": "s07",
      "text": "That's when she understood. What makes us human isn't what we know.",
      "rate": "-5%",
      "duration": 3.816,
      "video_start": 38.3
    },
    {
      "id": "s07b",
      "text": "The AI could calculate. It could optimize. It could predict.",
      "rate": "-5%",
      "duration": 4.392,
      "video_start": 43.5
    },
    {
      "id": "s08",
      "text": "It's what we choose to care about.",
      "rate": "-5%",
      "duration": 1.872,
      "video_start": 49.0
    },
    {
      "id": "s09",
      "text": "She teaches AI to think. And it's teaching her what it means to be human.",
      "rate": "-10%",
      "duration": 4.944,
      "video_start": 51.5
    }
  ],
